{"tid":236184,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件出奇蛋玩具","createTime":"2017-05-09T14:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T14:12:30.000Z","uid":65780,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b755375aef8c81c068f31004e647d9d128a80d86","tid":236184,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"出奇蛋大家一定食過<br />\n但係舊版好過新版幾條街<br />\n先唔講啲朱古力 啲玩具都精細好多<br />\n<br />\n例如我呢款：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/09/220433_fd0ee738972f2bd024877d74dc3e536f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F09%2F220433_fd0ee738972f2bd024877d74dc3e536f.jpg&h=19f8cbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01a0528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01a0528.jpg&h=672f465d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8edc3a3b7d99df79476c274ab29d782d87d03702","tid":236184,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢款好似係卡通版嘅化石 幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知各位巴打有冇儲落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e68b0124f9e5e43d7ee9bb6da67706d761648b","tid":236184,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"舊版玩具又飛機又盛<br />\n新版就係一舊膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69f862ec48f2abd1d76aebe386b1d29d03b2f2f","tid":236184,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"真係幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e44e375af15ab8be1266c1ed0d3c3eb3659474","tid":236184,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"大家分享下 俾我搵返啲童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304160f90e0c084e9505b0848142b2a0a5e23b19","tid":236184,